DB info in ezsql.php

Needs ffmpeg and imagemagick to be installed

Load schema.sql into a MySQL database

The file cron.php needs to be called as a cron.  


About this app:

It was installed on bluehost.com, so there's some limitations to the # of pics that can be made into a video.  Basically, bluehost had a limit on the amount of time a job can run.

This is a web app which authenticates your Smugmug and YouTube accounts, and then takes selected albums (or everything) and puts it in a video on YouTube.

Here's an example:

http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8W92UrUdvNY 
